name: Natural Anti-Aging Serum 1oz
description:
Formulated for mature skin to tone, balance, and replenish.
Rich in skin-loving ingredients to boost skin elasticity and prevent signs of aging. Ingredients: Aqua, Glycerin, Xanthan Gum, Polygonum Fagopyrum (Buckwheat) Seed Extract, Gigartina Stellata Extract, Panax Ginseng (Ginseng) Root Extract, Haematococcus Pluvialis (Green Algae) Extract, Lonicera Japonica (Japanese Honeysuckle) Flower Extract, Lonicera Caprifolium (Italian Honeysuckle) Flower Extract, Polysorbate-20
